&CWelcome to The Realms of Kuvia.

We are currently in the early stages of player testing, so please make extensive
use of the &WBUG&C, &WTYPO&C, and &WIDEA&C commands.  Most commands have help files,
though they are being reworked constantly.  You will also notice a [NEWS] prompt 
in front of your normal prompt, type &WNEWS&C to view the news files that you have
missed!

